    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right person? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who needs basic wheels, a project, or a dependable backup to have around. It\u2019s being priced fairly and sold honestly, with plenty of value here for a handy buyer who doesn\u2019t mind giving it a little TLC. If you want something inexpensive and straightforward, this could be a great fit.",
