      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "\"Driver-oriented project with strong bones and plenty of usable life left. The powertrain pulls through the rev range, the chassis feels planted, and it has the kind of honest mechanical character enthusiasts appreciate. Cosmetically it shows its age and it will benefit from continued sorting, but it\u2019s a solid budget entry for someone who wants affordable transportation, a weekend wrenching platform, or a parts-friendly build candidate. Hard to find this much potential at this price.\"",
